name: Thanks
description:
In the lavender fields this year many things happened, when at the beginning everything seemed to fall apart many friends arrived to help fix everything (we bunnies cried a lot) now everything is very nice and bloomed. 

---
Thank you very much for everything, I don't say it much but you all helped me to get up in every way and I want to thank you for being there, you changed my life. Sometimes it is difficult to deal with many things, and I was always anxious to show my pieces, but now it is very nice, thank you for embracing them 🌹🌹🌹

PS: Although many little animals live far away in other forests, it makes me happy to be able to send you this letter thanks to technology. 
I love you and thanks, ALWAYS 🐇
